{"000-section": {"000-title": "Rs. 1000 Cr Integrated Fisheries Development Scheme (IFDS) in Telangana"}, "001-section": {"000-title": "Telangana Integrated Fisheries Development Scheme (IFDS)", "001-normal": "The important features and highlights of TS Fisheries Development Scheme are as follows:-", "002-listElement": "- The state govt. will provide inputs like supply of fish seed, construction of landings for boats and catch near lakes, tanks and reservoirs at 100% subsidy.", "003-listElement": "- Under IFDS, people will get 75% subsidy to purchase high quality nets, two wheelers and luggage autos, vehicles for mobile shops to sell fish. In addition, Insulated vehicles will also attract subsidy for the transportation of the catch.", "004-listElement": "- IFDS Scheme also comprises of provision for the construction of hatcheries to raise fingerlings, setting up of fish feed manufacturing units, processing and ice manufacturing plants at 75% subsidy.", "005-listElement": "- IFDS will also include subsidy ranging from 80% to 90% to set up kiosks for selling fish, fish products & boats.", "006-listElement": "- A total number of 1,61,376 units will be provided to around 5000 beneficiaries under IFDS.", "007-normal": "CM KCR has launched this Integrated Fisheries Development Scheme (IFDS) on 5 Sept 2018 at People\u2019s plaza near Hussain Sagar. At the official launch event, families of 2 fishermen received an ex-gratia of Rs. 4 lakh each who have lost their bread winners in accidents."}, "002-section": {"000-title": "Objectives of IFDS Scheme in Telangana", "001-normal": "This scheme is being launched in accordance with the following objectives:-", "002-listElement": "- Increasing fish production and productivity by providing backward and forward linkages & enhancing livelihoods of fishers.", "003-listElement": "- To achieve self-sufficiency in production of fish seed.", "004-listElement": "- Ensuring availability of fish to the consumers at affordable prices and in hygenic conditions by improving the marketing infrastructure.", "005-listElement": "- Welfare of fishers.", "006-normal": "For more details, visit the official website http://fisheries.telangana.gov.in/ifd.php"}}